{"tid":280844,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"重慶紅衣男孩神秘死亡案件","createTime":"2017-06-12T10:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T21:52:20.000Z","uid":6061,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"620ca8fdb124af8cd637f4ef1bef744b3a40b5c3","tid":280844,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:14:40.000Z","msg":"2009年11月4日凌晨，在重慶江北區打工的巴南區東泉鎮雙星村村民匡紀祿的妻子在熟睡中做了一個奇怪的夢，睡夢中，她來到了他和丈夫在農村裏面住的老屋，忽然，一位從未謀面的陌生男子推門而入，不等她問清來由，這名男子便急忙催促他回家看一眼自己的兒子，正當她想湊近一些看清男子的真面目時，她猛然間從睡夢中驚醒。。。<br />\n<br />\n  甚感奇怪的匡紀祿妻子醒來後越想越不對勁，於是不顧正是凌晨時分，推醒了一旁熟睡的丈夫，向丈夫講述了剛才做的那個怪夢以及自己的擔憂。在她的再三催促下，丈夫答應向單位請個假，抽時間回家看一看自己留在老家獨自上學的兒子。一天後，也就是2009年11月5日，匡紀祿懷揣着給兒子的生活費趕回到了在巴南的老屋。可是這回與之前不同是，應該開着的正門和側門緊閉着，而一般不開的後門卻虛掩着。這奇怪的一幕讓匡紀祿聯想到了之前妻子和他談到的那個奇怪的夢，頓時一股不祥的預感從他心裏夾雜着寒氣升起。匡志軍三步並作兩步地趕到後門，一把推開，眼前的景象讓他大驚失色。<br />\n<br />\n  屋內，兒子雙手雙腳都被繩子綁着，懸吊在屋樑上，身上穿着別着白花的紅色裙子，裏面還穿着他堂姐的紅色泳衣。匡紀祿連忙上前，試圖將兒子從懸掛着的繩子上接下，但無奈兒子已經氣絕多時，匡紀祿唉聲嘆氣着，眼裏的淚水也是不住地往下掉。"},{"pid":"94c3ed5fefba361e16d3e1f1a98bf82004426aae","tid":280844,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:17:44.000Z","msg":"呢單超恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55579c641594f0f1b77c1847e0df1037bc1f35a","tid":280844,"uid":52590,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2660b2961abcab992ad08de6fe4442e787bf82","tid":280844,"uid":6061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:18:59.000Z","msg":"哭也哭過了，當務之急是趕緊報警，讓警方前來偵破此案，給自己的兒子一個交代<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n接到報案的警方火速地趕到了現場。經現場勘測警方發現，匡志均裏面貼身穿着一條紅色泳衣，外面穿着一條別着白花的紅裙子，腳上掛着一個鐵制秤砣，除此之外，自己的衣物一件也沒有穿。而在匡志均身上，除了因繩子肋出的印痕外，其他的幾乎沒有穿。一番忙碌之後，警方取走了匡志均的內臟，進行進一步化驗，以確定死因。<br />\n<br />\n自此之後，匡紀祿一家便等待着警方的消息，希望警方可以早日破案，緝拿真兇。但是，令匡紀祿家失望的是，他們苦等來的竟是警方對於匡志均死亡不予立案的消息，而在匡紀祿所拿到的戶口派出所出具的死亡戶口註銷證明上的「死亡原因」一欄，寫着：「其他意外死亡」，這「其他意外死亡」指的又是什麼死亡？"},{"pid":"d29dc7fee43c57f7a55d2124f27dcb49f79ad9ee","tid":280844,"uid":6061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:20:21.000Z","msg":"關於紅衣男孩的新聞報道<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於警方給出的兒子的死亡原因，匡紀祿當然不滿意，在他看來，兒子獨自在老屋中莫名其妙就死亡了，死亡的方式如此怪異，考慮到生前自家並未與人結怨且兒子也無怪癖，兒子的死亡還是有很多的蹊蹺之處可尋的。匡紀祿對於警方給出的「意外死亡」這一說法，提出了如下幾點疑問：「<span style=\"color: green;\">什麼叫意外死亡？既然不是他殺和自殺，我兒子究竟遇到了什麼意外？這種意外是怎麼出現的？</span>」懷揣着這些疑問，匡紀祿走進了重慶巴南區派出所，對於此案的結論申請複議，並以對於學生的失蹤沒有及時聯繫學生家長為由狀告匡志均生前所讀的學校。"},{"pid":"35ccd68a3b4e938dbab62940ec901b5ea4b19c5e","tid":280844,"uid":6061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:21:17.000Z","msg":"11月21日下午，匡紀祿來到警局，這天是他和警方約定的獲取複議結果的日子。可是，他再一次失望了，根據法醫的調查結果，警局給出了「維持原決定，屬意外身亡，仍然不予立案」的決定。而面對這樣一個決定，匡紀祿當場便提出了異議，他質問在場的警員：「兒子死時床上有一條新的鐵鏈子，家裏從來沒有這種鐵鏈，它從哪裏來的？現在又到哪裏去了？還有，平時家裏從來不開的後門，在兒子死後卻虛掩着，說明有人從屋裏出來。警方進去後，看到他人的腳印、手印沒有？我兒子平時從來不上網，他怎麼可能意外死亡？究竟他遇到了什麼意外？」。"},{"pid":"40494fefc733e21a50adabed04efc7baf6148114","tid":280844,"uid":6061,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:23:10.000Z","msg":"慎入 死者圖片：<a href=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/14d000348aed0857ce0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F14d000348aed0857ce0&d=7jmWbiLIIbdpf1IUmjmdyZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=89b3bf63\" target=\"_blank\">https://i1.kknews.cc/large/14d000348aed0857ce0</a>"},{"pid":"bf4b958588ebb94b1a4337ea6babe3ab25a2eeb2","tid":280844,"uid":107472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:23:40.000Z","msg":"唔係講左係類似巫術個d儀式咩  <br />\n個細路個八字好似極陰"},{"pid":"e8ef9e9803657239c8b30a41bfa76f6663d6eda1","tid":280844,"uid":188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:25:07.000Z","msg":"隔離d野五行做祭品阿麻"},{"pid":"1656609121f809e98d62898179e748d82d6ce5d7","tid":280844,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:26:12.000Z","msg":"因為在案發現場，警方既沒有發現犯罪嫌疑人的腳印，又沒有發現作案兇器，更未發現男孩身上有與人搏鬥的痕跡（比如說傷痕，或者血跡，又或者搏鬥時被打翻的物品等，一切皆無），周圍環境氣氛也頗為自然、祥和。那麼，紅衣男孩究竟是怎麼用繩子把自己的雙手捆住，並且自己吊在房梁之上的呢？恐怕非人力所為。<br />\n<br />\n匡志均遺體的額頭前有一個小孔和不重的外傷，大腿、雙手、兩肋、雙腳踝部上方都有較深的勒痕；此外沒有任何傷口。<br />\n<br />\n但隨着時間的推移，警方依舊沒能找到詳細、具體、明確、令人信服的證據、線索和理由。他們最後仍認定，紅衣男孩是自殺的。法醫也進行了解剖，認為這是一起窒息死亡的案件。"},{"pid":"2d47b333ffff062999b343e4f3a6233b34c2a8cd","tid":280844,"uid":6061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:33:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係講左係類似巫術個d儀式咩  <br />\n個細路個八字好似極陰</blockquote><br />\n從最初2009年底重慶男孩離奇死亡，有人推斷還要有12個人死亡 <br />\n現在莆田4人+天臺5人+天臺2人+電話亭遇害女孩1人，總共正好13人"},{"pid":"a465c0ca5e51c49ad8ab1ffeff8e73a67b84b17b","tid":280844,"uid":4328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:35:03.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4ecff80b2d74e5dcccd40dfcd7e67322f4dc5e99","tid":280844,"uid":6061,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隔離d野五行做祭品阿麻</blockquote><br />\nYes 最多人講係幫某人續命"},{"pid":"6df983650dc38f59b08e662c76243f1efcf9cf8c","tid":280844,"uid":107472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係講左係類似巫術個d儀式咩  <br />\n個細路個八字好似極陰</blockquote><br />\n從最初2009年底重慶男孩離奇死亡，有人推斷還要有12個人死亡 <br />\n現在莆田4人+天臺5人+天臺2人+電話亭遇害女孩1人，總共正好13人</blockquote><br />\n好邪門  咩人咁神通廣大  可以搵到咁多個八字極陰既細路黎開刀"},{"pid":"c41033a0526b6668e98d3e165820f17ae39f7326","tid":280844,"uid":9564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T10:47:10.000Z","msg":"當年怪談拍完呢一集之後就即刻宣布收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16377b33167012c066f3e93d1e9c557ee4bbc48","tid":280844,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T11:16:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=__QF1QGou2U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D__QF1QGou2U&d=7jmWbiLIIbdpf1IUmjmdyZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ea48b668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=__QF1QGou2U</a><br />\n<br />\n怪談"},{"pid":"a4a421b415f674c5ee2b9bd0733431ab8b2f28f0","tid":280844,"uid":6061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=__QF1QGou2U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D__QF1QGou2U&d=7jmWbiLIIbdpf1IUmjmdyZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ea48b668\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=__QF1QGou2U</a><br />\n<br />\n怪談</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ad98ef9686ff8b0a44ffd7c05cca19d7f40aa5","tid":280844,"uid":102880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隔離d野五行做祭品阿麻</blockquote><br />\nYes 最多人講係幫某人續命</blockquote><br />\n江<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50cb6b761f5a445537991ceaf99468e7e65639b0","tid":280844,"uid":41543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508fd64ca748cde614aecaa0bab6ba89c6f3ceb9","tid":280844,"uid":79471,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:33:22.000Z","msg":"ptt有篇預言<br />\n哩下先痴撚線"},{"pid":"5b757eb9795a709364745beb0fcd27bf8edc9d51","tid":280844,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:33:59.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b5614206b59dc6c7ecd481da15869a86d27596b8","tid":280844,"uid":23987,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ptt有篇預言<br />\n哩下先痴撚線</blockquote><br />\nMore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6e4f82fb4b870621ff46c3467af9957ce62912","tid":280844,"uid":31991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc894c6b54b46e2185c7c46d391f790555c5be4d","tid":280844,"uid":123056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ptt有篇預言<br />\n哩下先痴撚線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nF5"},{"pid":"a0ea31d9f669f60a9a48c5a990d2a51679d068d4","tid":280844,"uid":74021,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:41:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係講左係類似巫術個d儀式咩  <br />\n個細路個八字好似極陰</blockquote><br />\n從最初2009年底重慶男孩離奇死亡，有人推斷還要有12個人死亡 <br />\n現在莆田4人+天臺5人+天臺2人+電話亭遇害女孩1人，總共正好13人</blockquote><br />\n一樣死法？"},{"pid":"a8899b4fda42aed40f05519a37cb19a6c06b8938","tid":280844,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ptt有篇預言<br />\n哩下先痴撚線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nF5</blockquote><br />\n自膠 好似唔係預言<br />\n有馬後炮之嫌"},{"pid":"be6302635b440e817252797b29deffc1db073de8","tid":280844,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:44:11.000Z","msg":"lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03632a57416d409320f5200901487e94c8178bd2","tid":280844,"uid":5818,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係講左係類似巫術個d儀式咩  <br />\n個細路個八字好似極陰</blockquote><br />\n從最初2009年底重慶男孩離奇死亡，有人推斷還要有12個人死亡 <br />\n現在莆田4人+天臺5人+天臺2人+電話亭遇害女孩1人，總共正好13人</blockquote><br />\n一樣死法？</blockquote><br />\nWiki:<br />\n有網友認為取得「至陰」的魂魄一共要殺13個同樣命格的人，恰好在2009年末到2010年初在中國發生多起青少年離奇死亡事件，例如2010年2月4日福建莆田溺斃4人，2010年2月18日浙江天台溺死5人，2010年3月2日福建莆田某電話亭有一名女孩吊死在其中，而同一天浙江天台又溺死2人。經過網友分析，認為這13人中有11人的死亡與「水」有關，而吊死的2人「五行屬水」[2]。有人進一步分析認為此一系列事件利用了所謂「七星燈續命術」，這一系列事件都是為了給某一個「總格為水」的大人物續命。"},{"pid":"e8ca8e2e5d7d04c5b4403642385c4873510b5c2a","tid":280844,"uid":14191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:46:00.000Z","msg":"以為野火巴打開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw, momo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a73b7ee75c697aa0059a27d8920b77e4d8f6ec","tid":280844,"uid":7823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ptt有篇預言<br />\n哩下先痴撚線</blockquote><br />\nMore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9722c2111b393fe898000aee2da5f8cf07d2ef","tid":280844,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:46:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/marvel/M.1265172655.A.41E.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Fmarvel%2FM.1265172655.A.41E.html&d=7jmWbiLIIbdpf1IUmjmdyZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=61b9f370\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/marvel/M.1265172655.A.41E.html</a>"},{"pid":"9c5b3c6296adc023b3adf8cd1641606158447b3e","tid":280844,"uid":51388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:48:44.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"5b5cf3fa2c33ec2ac5f12dd2045159b52ca6d7ce","tid":280844,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:49:35.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"55cfe38ac44b4efa69e068e9d800f854590da144","tid":280844,"uid":55664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b4cfee54e80fafc4d4b