By":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:11:27.000Z","msg":"江 澤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b4ed22a29af856e3aff3521a9663a34a75f73a","tid":280844,"uid":23592,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:24:44.000Z","msg":"冮凙冺？"},{"pid":"e4f0314a22d1758fc27a9576c73ee10e4ed6c852","tid":280844,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12308cac91a8995036a80335d72ecfc55a3f663","tid":280844,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:40:29.000Z","msg":"李曼筠真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d60d2d04438dfad28c5400b8477280d9668002f","tid":280844,"uid":23377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> lm"},{"pid":"c00459abc67ddbfe87eff9042fe4eb15277e8721","tid":280844,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4f604c4db9a91c4a705e04ccb6940836ead055","tid":280844,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"體位性性窒息死亡嘅可能性到底有幾高?<br />\n其實幾可信"},{"pid":"551344832904b5b8787b904b0976cb23fbb79819","tid":280844,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe001077e691a28970721541f5160cd6f61b08b","tid":280844,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:01:57.000Z","msg":"Lm好驚"},{"pid":"5bbea91a46ff169758322aa49de4f5d75e2e9150","tid":280844,"uid":50660,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:04:23.000Z","msg":"會唔會係父母想長命，賊喊抓賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b6edfe5863a9b23ee336ce68ac628d8d893761","tid":280844,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:05:53.000Z","msg":"係回旋處過馬路比車撞果個其實都係風水陣黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fdcf46871b045ea06beec8e96365b90548ae09","tid":280844,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6619a758cce7e77b7f8fe4b5affc411410342a8c","tid":280844,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係講左係類似巫術個d儀式咩  <br />\n個細路個八字好似極陰</blockquote><br />\n從最初2009年底重慶男孩離奇死亡，有人推斷還要有12個人死亡 <br />\n現在莆田4人+天臺5人+天臺2人+電話亭遇害女孩1人，總共正好13人</blockquote><br />\n一樣死法？</blockquote><br />\nWiki:<br />\n有網友認為取得「至陰」的魂魄一共要殺13個同樣命格的人，恰好在2009年末到2010年初在中國發生多起青少年離奇死亡事件，例如2010年2月4日福建莆田溺斃4人，2010年2月18日浙江天台溺死5人，2010年3月2日福建莆田某電話亭有一名女孩吊死在其中，而同一天浙江天台又溺死2人。經過網友分析，認為這13人中有11人的死亡與「水」有關，而吊死的2人「五行屬水」[2]。有人進一步分析認為此一系列事件利用了所謂「七星燈續命術」，這一系列事件都是為了給某一個「總格為水」的大人物續命。</blockquote><br />\n中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5534b56e1826fbab86a1b9de4b33bbfb2ef0acf","tid":280844,"uid":65378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"MORE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f851817dcfed2c96cf690f8676a8b8f9839ec27","tid":280844,"uid":11